HEADWORD: micrometeorite
<hw>micrometeorite</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A meteorite so small that it
drifts down to Earth without becoming intensely heated in the earth's
atmosphere.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>micrometeoritic</ent>⟦br⟧
